Table C_PIB_SVMXC_DEVICE_HISTORY

Card of table C_PIB_SVMXC_DEVICE_HISTORY

Name

C_PIB_SVMXC_DEVICE_HISTORY


Description of the table C_PIB_SVMXC_DEVICE_HISTORY

20-Nov-2022

 

History of changes to tracked fields in ServiceMax. Changes recorded at timestamp level. RECORD_START_DATETIME, RECORD_END_DATETIME.

 

Source: SVMXC_Installed_product_history__c

History of creation of the record is not included.

 

Current value of the field for the equipment , IS_LAST_VERSION = Y

RECORD_START_DATE to RECORD_END_DATE - the value in NEW_VALUE is active for the equipment.

 

Update Frequency: Daily for SystemModStamp

 

Known Issue: changes are record against both the Device Id and the device Name, which will appear as a duplicate.
